<hr>
<strong>REFERENCE ENTRY</strong>
<br>
<br>
Add a reference at the end of your essay citing all relevant sources used in your research.
<br>
<br>
When URLs are longer than one line, if necessary, break a URL at a slash. For further information, 
refer to 
<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK7269/box/A55019/?report=objectonly" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
	Citing Medicine, chapter 22</a>.
<br>
<br>
If the place of publication is not included in the document use square brackets. For further 
information refer to  
<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK7267/box/A39606/?report=objectonly" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
	Citing Medicine, chapter 5</a>.
<br>
<br>
<strong>Format</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref" style="padding-left: 0px;">
	<ol start="8" style="margin-left: 0px;">
		<li class="ref-pad-0-13cm">
			Author Initial(s). Title of Thesis [Type of thesis]. [Place of publication]: Name of University;  
			Year of publication.
		</li>
	</ol>
</blockquote>
<br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref" style="padding-left: 0px;">
	<ol start="8" style="margin-left: 0px;">
		<li class="ref-pad-0-13cm">
			<span class="hover" title="Author">Gale</span>
			<span class="hover" title="Initial(s)">L</span>.
			<span class="hover" title="Title of Thesis">The relationship between leadership and employee empowerment for successful total quality management</span> 
			<span class="hover" title="Type of thesis">[PhD thesis]</span>.
			<span class="hover" title="Place of publication">[Penrith (AU)]</span>:
			<span class="hover" title="Name of University">University of Western Sydney</span>;
			<span class="hover" title="Year of publication">2000</span>.
		</li>
	</ol>
</blockquote>
<br>
If the thesis is available in electronic format, add the medium, date cited and URL.
<br>
<br>
<strong>Example</strong>
<br>
<blockquote class="ref" style="padding-left: 0px;">
	<ol start="8" style="margin-left: 0px;">
		<li class="ref-pad-0-13cm">
			<span class="hover" title="Author">Gale</span>
			<span class="hover" title="Initial(s)">L</span>.
			<span class="hover" title="Title of Thesis">The relationship between leadership and employee empowerment for successful total quality management</span> 
			<span class="hover" title="Type of thesis">[PhD thesis on the internet]</span>.
			<span class="hover" title="Place of publication">[Penrith (AU)]</span>:
			<span class="hover" title="Name of University">University of Western Sydney</span>;
			<span class="hover" title="Year of publication">2000</span>
			<span class="hover" title="Date cited">[cited 2002 Nov 24]</span>.
			Available from: <span class="hover" title="Available from">http://handle.uws.edu.au:8081/1959.7/28037</span>
		</li>
	</ol>
</blockquote>
